quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Nahin main kasam khata hoon qayamat ke din ki
  75,2,"Aur nahin,main kasam khata hoon malamat karne wale nafs ki"
  75,3,Kya Insan yeh samajh raha hai ke hum uski haddiyon ko jama na kar sakengey
  75,4,Kyun nahin? Hum to uski ungliyon ke por por tak theek bana dene par qadir hain
  75,5,Magar Insan chahta yeh hai ke aagey bhi badh-aamaliyan karta rahey
  75,6,“Puchta hai” aakhir kab aana hai woh qayamat ka din
  75,7,Phir jab dedhey pathra jayengey (sight is dazed)
  75,8,Aur chand be-noor ho jayega
  75,9,Aur Chand Suraj mila kar ek kardiya jayenge
  75,10,Us waqt yahi Insan kahega kahan bhaag kar jaun
  75,11,"Hargiz nahin,wahan koi jaye panaah na hogi"
  75,12,Us roz terey Rubb hi ke samney jaakar theharna hoga
  75,13,Us roz Insan ko uska sab agla pichla kiya karaya bata diya jayega
  75,14,Balke Insan khud hi apne aap ko khoob janta hai
  75,15,Chahey woh kitni hi maazratein (excuses) karey
  75,16,"Aey Nabi , Is wahi ko jaldi jaldi yaad karne ke liye apni zubaan ko harkat na do"
  75,17,Isko yaad kara dena aur padhwa dena hamare zimmey hai
  75,18,Lihaza jab hum isey padh rahey hon us waqt tum iske qirat ko gaur se sunte raho
  75,19,Phir iska matlab samjha dena bhi hamarey zimmey hai
  75,20,"Hargiz nahin, asal baat yeh hai ke tum log jaldi haasil honay wali cheez (yani duniya) se muhabbat rakhte ho"
  75,21,Aur aakhirat ko chodh dete ho
  75,22,Us roz kuch chehrey tar-o-taza hongey
  75,23,Apne Rubb ki taraf dekh rahey hongey
  75,24,Aur kuch chehrey udas hongey
  75,25,Aur samajh rahey hongey ke unke saath qamar-todh bartao hone wala hai
  75,26,"Hargiz nahin, jab jaan halaq tak pahunch jayegi"
  75,27,Aur kaha jayega ke hai koi jhaad phook karne wala
  75,28,Aur aadmi samajh lega ke yeh duniya se judai ka waqt hai
  75,29,Aur pindli(leg) se pindli(leg) judh jayegi
  75,30,Woh din hoga tere Rubb ki taraf rawangi ka
  75,31,"Magar usne na sach mana , aur na namaz padhi"
  75,32,Balke jhutlaya aur palat gaya
  75,33,Phir akadta hua apne ghar walon ki taraf chal diya
  75,34,Yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,35,Haan yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,36,"Kya Insan ne yeh samajh rakkha hai ke woh yunhi mohmal (left alone, unquestioned )chodh diya jayega"
  75,37,Kya woh ek hakeer pani ka nutfa (sperm from semen) na tha jo (raham –e-madar mei) tapkaya jata hai
  75,38,"Phir woh ek lothda(clot) bana, phir Allah ne uska jism banaya aur uske aazaa durust kiye"
  75,39,Phir ussey mard aur aurat ki do qismein banayi
  75,40,Kya woh ispar qadir nahin hai ke marne walon ko phir zinda karde